nodes.title: Workflow Information
widgets_values:
Improved Searge SDXL workflow for SDXL 1.0 - INPAINTING - created on Jul 27, 2023

To use this workflow, set up ComfyUI like this:

- Install the Searge SDXL custom node extension from https://github.com/SeargeDP/SeargeSDXL
  - open the command line in directory: ComfyUI/custom_nodes
  - run the command: git clone https://github.com/SeargeDP/SeargeSDXL.git
  - restart ComfyUI

SDXL 1.0 base:
 https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/stable-diffusion-xl-base-1.0/resolve/main/sd_xl_base_1.0.safetensors
SDXL 1.0 refiner:
 https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/stable-diffusion-xl-refiner-1.0/resolve/main/sd_xl_refiner_1.0.safetensors

SDXL 0.9 vae:  https://huggingface.co/madebyollin/sdxl-vae-fp16-fix/resolve/main/sdxl_vae.safetensors
4x-UltraSharp upscaler:  https://huggingface.co/uwg/upscaler/resolve/main/ESRGAN/4x-UltraSharp.pth
4x_NMKD-Siax_200k upscaler:  https://huggingface.co/uwg/upscaler/resolve/main/ESRGAN/4x_NMKD-Siax_200k.pth

Image sizes that are "ideal" for different aspect ratios:
    | 1024x1024 | 1152x896 | 896x1152 | 1216x832 | 832x1216 | 1344x768 | 768x1344 | 1536x640 | 640x1536 |
